Create Near
SyncState *

# josefkruer@gmail.com
MaildirStore josefkruer@gmail.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/josefkruer@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/mail/josefkruer@gmail.com/INBOX

IMAPStore josefkruer@gmail.com-remote
AuthMechs LOGIN
Host imap.gmail.com
User josefkruer@gmail.com
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
SSLType IMAPS
PassCmd "pass show google-app"

Channel josefkruer@gmail.com
Far :josefkruer@gmail.com-remote:
Near :josefkruer@gmail.com-local:
Patterns *
Sync PullNew PullFlags

